To install for standard use 

    python setup.py install

to install for development 

    python setup.py develop


Notes:

To use the LaTeX printing options in galgebra a LaTeX distibution is required 
containing pdflatex (texlive for linux, miktex for windows).

To use the enhances printing options in windows ansicon must be installed -

github.com/adoxa/ansicon

It is strongly reccomended that the geany editor/development environment be installed -

www.geany.org

for developing code using galgebra.



